gland</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_England_to_1483\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of England to 1483\">to 1483</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_England,_1485%E2%80%931601\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of England, 1485\u20131601\">1485\u20131601</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_England,_1603%E2%80%931641\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of England, 1603\u20131641\">1603\u20131641</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Ordinances_and_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_England,_1642%E2%80%931660\" title=\"List of Ordinances and Acts of the Parliament of England, 1642\u20131660\">Interregnum (1642\u20131660)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_England,_1660%E2%80%931699\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of England, 1660\u20131699\">1660\u20131699</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_England,_1700%E2%80%931706\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of England, 1700\u20131706\">1700\u20131706</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Parliament of Scotland</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_Scotland_to_1707\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of Scotland to 1707\">to 1707</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Acts of Parliament of the<br /><a href=\"/wiki/Kingdom_of_Great_Britain\" title=\"Kingdom of Great Britain\">Kingdom of Great Britain</a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_Great_Britain,_1707%E2%80%931719\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of Great Britain, 1707\u20131719\">1707\u20131719</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_Great_Britain,_1720%E2%80%931739\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of Great Britain, 1720\u20131739\">1720\u20131739</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_Great_Britain,_1740%E2%80%931759\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of Great Britain, 1740\u20131759\">1740\u20131759</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_Great_Britain,_1760%E2%80%931779\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of Great Britain, 1760\u20131779\">1760\u20131779</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_Great_Britain,_1780%E2%80%931800\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of Great Britain, 1780\u20131800\">1780\u20131800</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Acts of the <a href=\"/wiki/Parliament_of_Ireland\" title=\"Parliament of Ireland\">Parliament of Ireland</a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_Ireland_to_1700\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of Ireland to 1700\">to 1700</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Parliament_of_Ireland,_1701%E2%80%931800\" title=\"List of Acts of the Parliament of Ireland, 1701\u20131800\">1701\u20131800</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Act_of_Parliament_(UK)\" title=\"Act of Parliament (UK)\">Acts of Parliament</a> of the <a href=\"/wiki/United_Kingdom_o